const specialties = ["Cardiology", "Orthopedics", "Pediatrics", "Neurology", "Dermatology", "Primary Care"]; const locations = ["New York, NY", "Los Angeles, CA", "Chicago, IL", "Houston, TX", "Boston, MA"]; const LandingPage = () => { const [isVisible, setIsVisible] = useState(false); const [currentData, setCurrentData] = useState(sampleData.slice(0, 3)); const [searchText, setSearchText] = useState(""); const [selectedSpecialty, setSelectedSpecialty] = useState(0); const [selectedLocation, setSelectedLocation] = useState(0); useEffect(() => { setIsVisible(true); // Animate data changes const dataInterval = setInterval(() => { setCurrentData(prev => { const newData = [...sampleData]; return newData.sort(() => Math.random() - 0.5).slice(0, 3); }); }, 3000); // Animate search text const searchInterval = setInterval(() => { setSearchText(specialties[selectedSpecialty]); setSelectedSpecialty((prev) => (prev + 1) % specialties.length); }, 2000); // Animate location filter const locationInterval = setInterval(() => { setSelectedLocation((prev) => (prev + 1) % locations.length); }, 4000); return () => { clearInterval(dataInterval); clearInterval(searchInterval); clearInterval(locationInterval); }; }, []); return (
